==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unmoral
<hw>Un*mor"al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having no moral
perception, quality, or relation; involving no idea of morality; --
distinguished from both <xex>moral</xex> and <xex>immoral</xex>.</def>
-- <wordforms><wf>Un`mo*ral"i*ty</wf> <pr>(#)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unmoralized</ent>⟦br⟧
